snippet.title: Urban Constructor - PlayStation 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
This was Phoenix Games' attempt at a Qix clone, but themed after the urban cities and construction sites. Weirdly, it reminds me of Urbanix, a PSP minis and WiiWare game that shares the similar theme and is also a Qix clone.

#retrogames #retrogaming #playstation2 #ps2 #phoenixgames #urbanconstructor
